audio_descriptions.notes: The scene starts off at a pool party where a boy in a green shirt cannon bombs into the water. The pool is filled with people in and outside, water splashing everywhere and children playing marco polo. The scene then focuses on a three ladies tanning off to the side all wearing black sunglasses and bathing suits. when one says "shes coming down" then all the attention is focused to the lifeguard. Then approaches a man in his 20s shirtless, wearing red shorts and black sunglasses, with long hair that reached his shoulders. The three woman daze at the man and are lost looking at him. As the man lifeguard walks to his podium he greets the woman after telling the boy in the green shirt he shall not be allowed to jump. He then continues to climb onto his podium and sit there while the woman are still staring at him.
